         <note class="- topic/note ">If the battery has 4 poles
connect the cable to all poles. If the battery has more than 4 poles
it is sufficient to connect the measuring cable to only 4 poles. Use
the same poles at each battery.</note>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To attach the BC4Cxx measuring
cable to the battery:</p>
